Name: SpiderClimber
About the game: SpiderClimber is a role-playing adventure game SpiderClimber has advanced physics engine and innovative operation. Every hill, branch and stone can bring you many challenges. find your way home with just one thread. looking for the meaning of life in constant failures and setbacks. Lost, back again and again, this journey home seems to be painful, 60% of our testers, struggling on the ground for 30 minutes or more, 80% lost for 1 hour or more, good luck. unexpected rewards are waiting for the little spider.
